title: Bobby And His Girlfriend Throw Amy A Birthday Party! + Dr. William Schaffner Answers Coronavirus Questions + Jordan Davis Talks About Flying Back From the UK
itunes:title: Bobby And His Girlfriend Throw Amy A Birthday Party! + Dr. William Schaffner Answers Coronavirus Questions + Jordan Davis Talks About Flying Back From the UK
description:
Bobby and his girlfriend threw Amy a small birthday party last night, but also practiced social distancing and kept it to just three people. Dr. William Schaffner is a disease expert. He joined the show today to answer our Coronavirus questions and address some of the rumors. Plus, country artist Jordan Davis talked about a scary situation he had while flying to London.
